{"tid":234963,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"咪再屌柒人哋移民","createTime":"2017-05-08T15:58:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-11T02:37:38.000Z","uid":2200,"like":11,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a04ac30c9d9f34ae1783c019067b7d5baa616176","tid":234963,"uid":2200,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T15:58:49.000Z","msg":"成日話香港係我哋家<br />\n做咩要走<br />\n走咗就係垃圾<br />\n其實當你每日發現自己越來越絕望<br />\n啲樓日日升<br />\n只有個大學學位/有少少技術但無乜錢，你會寧願去外國重新嚟過<br />\n<br />\n係呀，去到外國係變做小數<br />\n可能融入唔到<br />\n但係10年之後，香港就已經全部都係支那狗，講支那話，啲學生大個全部都係蝗<br />\n咁講廣東話都係少數啦<br />\n<br />\n人各有志，我等緊年尾走<br />\n就快頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fa65be7b40e3d2d0ef73fafaa4c8e3433c1fc71","tid":234963,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T16:01:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37622a25c44c9daae4bb69f993d80c9885bfbf20","tid":234963,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T16:01:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d9fe80ea679d843d99b5781cbd5b1ad68c212b98","tid":234963,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T16:15:45.000Z","msg":"帶頭叫民主回歸<br />\n爭取真雙普選人<br />\n多數係離地一族"},{"pid":"eb9663d25a29205cb97945f851543283301c7506","tid":234963,"uid":2200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T16:19:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>帶頭叫民主回歸<br />\n爭取真雙普選人<br />\n多數係離地一族</blockquote><br />\n票又投過<br />\n咁點<br />\n有大部分人都要民主中国<br />\n保皇嘅繼續保皇<br />\n其實好多人已經淨係care買樓<br />\n政治生態極唔健康<br />\n<br />\n到生小朋友<br />\n一係多蝗<br />\n一係就要繼續玩呢個鬥爭遊戲<br />\n<br />\n利申：靠教育搵快錢，但真係好無奈"},{"pid":"93ad2494196e9c8bfdb64cbd35d58eca67c2fc0c","tid":234963,"